<paragraph blockId="1.[189,303,1762,1788]" box="[189,303,1762,1788]" pageId="1" pageNumber="2">
<heading bold="true" box="[189,303,1762,1788]" fontSize="11" level="3" pageId="1" pageNumber="2" reason="3">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[189,303,1762,1788]" pageId="1" pageNumber="2">Remarks</emphasis>
</heading>
</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="1.[189,1399,1808,2011]" lastBlockId="2.[189,1398,266,362]" lastPageId="2" lastPageNumber="3" pageId="1" pageNumber="2">
Most workers (e.g., 
<bibRefCitation author="Gordon I." box="[436,599,1808,1834]" pageId="1" pageNumber="2" pagination="201 - 253" refId="ref8477" refString="Gordon I. 1950. Crustacea Dromiacea. Part I: Systematic account of the Dromiacea collected by the &quot; John Murray &quot; Expedition. Part II. The morphology of the spermatheca in certain Dromiacea. Scientific Reports of the John Murray Expedition 1933 - 34 9 (3): 201 - 253." type="journal article" year="1950">Gordon 1950</bibRefCitation>
; 
<bibRefCitation author="Serene R. &amp; Lohavanijaya P." box="[614,971,1808,1834]" pageId="1" pageNumber="2" pagination="1 - 187" refId="ref8914" refString="Serene R. &amp; Lohavanijaya P. 1973. The Brachyura (Crustacea: Decapoda) collected by the Naga Expedition, including a review of the Homolidae. In: Brinton E., Newman W. A. &amp; Wooster W. S. (eds) Scientific Results of Marine Investigations of the South China Sea and the Gulf of Thailand, 1959 - 1961. Naga Report 4 (4): 1 - 187." type="journal article" year="1973">Serène &amp; Lohavanijaya 1973</bibRefCitation>
; 
<bibRefCitation author="Guinot D. &amp; Richer De Forges B." box="[987,1394,1808,1834]" pageId="1" pageNumber="2" pagination="283 - 517" refId="ref8571" refString="Guinot D. &amp; Richer De Forges B. 1995. Crustacea Decapoda Brachyura: Revision de la famille des Homolidae de Haan, 1839. In: Crosnier A. (ed.) Resultats des Campagnes MUSORSTOM, Vol. 13. Memoires du Museum national d'Histoire naturelle 163: 283 - 517. Museum national d'Histoire naturelle, Paris." type="journal article" year="1995">Guinot &amp; Richer de Forges 1995</bibRefCitation>
; 
<bibRefCitation author="Ahyong S. T. &amp; Naruse T. &amp; Tan S. H. &amp; Ng P. K. L." box="[189,424,1844,1870]" pageId="1" pageNumber="2" pagination="27 - 180" refId="ref8237" refString="Ahyong S. T., Naruse T., Tan S. H. &amp; Ng P. K. L. 2009. Part II. Infraorder Brachyura: Sections Dromiacea, Raninoida, Cyclodorippoida. In: Chan T. - Y., Ng P. K. L., Ahyong S. T. &amp; Tan S. H. (eds) Crustacean Fauna of Taiwan: Brachyuran Crabs, Vol. I: 27 - 180. National Taiwan Ocean University, Keelung, Taiwan." type="book chapter" year="2009">
Ahyong 
<emphasis box="[292,353,1844,1870]" italics="true" pageId="1" pageNumber="2">et al.</emphasis>
2009
</bibRefCitation>
; 
<bibRefCitation author="Garassino A." box="[437,623,1844,1870]" pageId="1" pageNumber="2" pagination="1 - 80" refId="ref8422" refString="Garassino A. 2009. The thoracic sternum and spermatheca in the extant genera of the family Homolidae De Haan, 1839 (Crustacea, Decapoda, Brachyura). Memorie della Societa Italiana di Scienze Naturali e del Museo Civico di Storia Naturale di Milano 36 (3): 1 - 80." type="journal article" year="2009">Garassino 2009</bibRefCitation>
) cite the author of 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Barnard" authorityYear="1946" box="[854,945,1844,1870]" class="Malacostraca" family="Homolidae" genus="Moloha" kingdom="Animalia" order="Decapoda" pageId="1" pageNumber="2" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis box="[854,945,1844,1870]" italics="true" pageId="1" pageNumber="2">Moloha</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
as “Barnard, 1947”. This is incorrect. 
<bibRefCitation author="Evenhuis N. L." box="[189,381,1879,1905]" pageId="1" pageNumber="2" pagination="1 - 68" refId="ref8387" refString="Evenhuis N. L. 2003. Publication and dating of the journals forming the Annals and Magazine of Natural History and the Journal of Natural History. Zootaxa 385: 1 - 68." type="journal article" year="2003">Evenhuis (2003)</bibRefCitation>
dated the volume of the journal concerned as 
<date box="[911,1074,1879,1905]" pageId="1" pageNumber="2" value="1946-04-29">
29 April 
<date box="[1012,1074,1879,1905]" pageId="1" pageNumber="2" value="1946" year="1946">1946</date>
</date>
. The genus should therefore be cited as 
<taxonomicName authority="Barnard, 1946" authorityName="Barnard" authorityYear="1946" box="[315,580,1914,1940]" class="Malacostraca" family="Homolidae" genus="Moloha" kingdom="Animalia" order="Decapoda" pageId="1" pageNumber="2" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis box="[315,406,1914,1940]" italics="true" pageId="1" pageNumber="2">Moloha</emphasis>
<bibRefCitation author="Barnard K. H." box="[411,580,1914,1940]" pageId="1" pageNumber="2" pagination="361 - 392" refId="ref8331" refString="Barnard K. H. 1946. Descriptions of new species of South African decapod Crustacea, with notes on synonymy and new records. Annals and Magazine of Natural History, Series 11, 13 (102): 361 - 392. http: // dx. doi. org / 10.1080 / 00222934608654562" type="journal article" year="1946">Barnard, 1946</bibRefCitation>
</taxonomicName>
. In that paper, Barnard also described two new genera (
<taxonomicName box="[1212,1350,1914,1940]" class="Malacostraca" family="Dromiidae" genus="Eudromidia" kingdom="Animalia" order="Decapoda" pageId="1" pageNumber="2" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis box="[1212,1350,1914,1940]" italics="true" pageId="1" pageNumber="2">Eudromidia</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
and 
<taxonomicName box="[189,329,1949,1975]" class="Malacostraca" family="Dromiidae" genus="Speodromia" kingdom="Animalia" order="Decapoda" pageId="1" pageNumber="2" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis box="[189,329,1949,1975]" italics="true" pageId="1" pageNumber="2">Speodromia</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
) and 10 new species (
<taxonomicName box="[594,827,1949,1975]" class="Malacostraca" family="Dromiidae" genus="Dromidia" kingdom="Animalia" order="Decapoda" pageId="1" pageNumber="2" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="aegibotus">
<emphasis box="[594,827,1949,1975]" italics="true" pageId="1" pageNumber="2">
Dromidia 
<taxonomicName box="[714,827,1949,1975]" pageId="1" pageNumber="2" rank="species" species="aegibotus">aegibotus</taxonomicName>
</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
, 
<taxonomicName box="[843,995,1949,1976]" class="Malacostraca" family="Dromiidae" genus="Dromidia" kingdom="Animalia" order="Decapoda" pageId="1" pageNumber="2" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="dissothrix">
<emphasis box="[843,995,1949,1976]" italics="true" pageId="1" pageNumber="2">
D. 
<taxonomicName box="[880,995,1949,1975]" pageId="1" pageNumber="2" rank="species" species="dissothrix">dissothrix</taxonomicName>
</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
, 
<taxonomicName box="[1010,1267,1949,1976]" class="Malacostraca" family="Dromiidae" genus="Dromidiopsis" kingdom="Animalia" order="Decapoda" pageId="1" pageNumber="2" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="cornuta">
<emphasis box="[1010,1267,1949,1976]" italics="true" pageId="1" pageNumber="2">
Dromidiopsis 
<taxonomicName box="[1176,1267,1951,1976]" pageId="1" pageNumber="2" rank="species" species="cornuta">cornuta</taxonomicName>
</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
(at present 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Stimpson" authorityYear="1858" box="[189,301,1984,2010]" class="Malacostraca" family="Dromiidae" genus="Dromidia" kingdom="Animalia" order="Decapoda" pageId="1" pageNumber="2" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis box="[189,301,1984,2010]" italics="true" pageId="1" pageNumber="2">Dromidia</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
), 
<taxonomicName authority="" authorityName="Barnard" authorityYear="1946" box="[324,658,1984,2010]" class="Malacostraca" family="Pleocyemata incertae sedis" genus="Cryptodromidiopsis" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Decapoda" pageId="1" pageNumber="2" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="lepidota">
<emphasis box="[324,658,1984,2010]" italics="true" pageId="1" pageNumber="2">
Cryptodromidiopsis 
<taxonomicName box="[563,658,1984,2010]" pageId="1" pageNumber="2" rank="species" species="lepidota">lepidota</taxonomicName>
</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
(at present 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Stimpson" authorityYear="1858" box="[791,903,1984,2010]" class="Malacostraca" family="Dromiidae" genus="Dromidia" kingdom="Animalia" order="Decapoda" pageId="1" pageNumber="2" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis box="[791,903,1984,2010]" italics="true" pageId="1" pageNumber="2">Dromidia</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
), 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Barnard" authorityYear="1947" box="[926,1142,1984,2011]" class="Malacostraca" family="Hexapodidae" genus="Hexapus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Decapoda" pageId="1" pageNumber="2" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="stebbingi">
<emphasis box="[926,1142,1984,2011]" italics="true" pageId="1" pageNumber="2">
Hexapus 
<taxonomicName box="[1035,1142,1984,2010]" pageId="1" pageNumber="2" rank="species" species="stebbingi">stebbingi</taxonomicName>
</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
(at present 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Manning &amp; Holthuis" authorityYear="1981" box="[1275,1382,1984,2010]" class="Malacostraca" family="Hexapodidae" genus="Tritoplax" kingdom="Animalia" order="Decapoda" pageId="1" pageNumber="2" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis box="[1275,1382,1984,2010]" italics="true" pageId="1" pageNumber="2">Tritoplax</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
), 
<taxonomicName box="[189,408,266,292]" class="Malacostraca" family="Hymenosomatidae" genus="Rhynchoplax" higherTaxonomySource="CoL" kingdom="Animalia" order="Decapoda" pageId="2" pageNumber="3" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="bovis">
<emphasis box="[189,408,266,292]" italics="true" pageId="2" pageNumber="3">
Rhynchoplax 
<taxonomicName box="[347,408,266,292]" pageId="2" pageNumber="3" rank="species" species="bovis">bovis</taxonomicName>
</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
(at present 
<taxonomicName box="[542,734,266,292]" class="Malacostraca" family="Hymenosomatidae" genus="Neorhynchoplax" kingdom="Animalia" order="Decapoda" pageId="2" pageNumber="3" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis box="[542,734,266,292]" italics="true" pageId="2" pageNumber="3">Neorhynchoplax</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
), 
<taxonomicName box="[757,1011,266,292]" class="Malacostraca" family="Leucosiidae" genus="Heteronucia" kingdom="Animalia" order="Decapoda" pageId="2" pageNumber="3" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="angulata">
<emphasis box="[757,1011,266,292]" italics="true" pageId="2" pageNumber="3">Heteronucia angulata</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
, 
<taxonomicName authority="M'Leay, 1838" authorityName="M'Leay" authorityYear="1838" box="[1024,1272,266,292]" class="Malacostraca" family="Epialtidae" genus="Dehaanius" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Decapoda" pageId="2" pageNumber="3" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="undulatus">
<emphasis box="[1024,1272,266,292]" italics="true" pageId="2" pageNumber="3">Dehaanius undulatus</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
(at present 
<taxonomicName box="[189,327,301,327]" class="Malacostraca" family="Epialtidae" genus="Acanthonyx" kingdom="Animalia" order="Decapoda" pageId="2" pageNumber="3" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis box="[189,327,301,327]" italics="true" pageId="2" pageNumber="3">Acanthonyx</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
), 
<taxonomicName box="[351,578,301,327]" class="Malacostraca" family="Portunidae" genus="Portumnus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Decapoda" pageId="2" pageNumber="3" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="mcleayi">
<emphasis box="[351,578,301,327]" italics="true" pageId="2" pageNumber="3">Portumnus mcleayi</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
(at present 
<taxonomicName authorityName="MacLeay" authorityYear="1838" box="[717,785,302,327]" class="Malacostraca" family="Portunidae" genus="Xaiva" kingdom="Animalia" order="Decapoda" pageId="2" pageNumber="3" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis box="[717,785,302,327]" italics="true" pageId="2" pageNumber="3">Xaiva</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
) and 
<taxonomicName box="[852,1025,301,327]" class="Malacostraca" family="Xanthidae" genus="Lybia" kingdom="Animalia" order="Decapoda" pageId="2" pageNumber="3" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="plumosa">
<emphasis box="[852,1025,301,327]" italics="true" pageId="2" pageNumber="3">Lybia plumosa</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
) from 
<collectingCountry box="[1107,1260,301,327]" name="South Africa" pageId="2" pageNumber="3">South Africa</collectingCountry>
. The author and date for all these taxa should be “ 
<bibRefCitation author="Barnard K. H." box="[624,796,336,362]" pageId="2" pageNumber="3" pagination="361 - 392" refId="ref8331" refString="Barnard K. H. 1946. Descriptions of new species of South African decapod Crustacea, with notes on synonymy and new records. Annals and Magazine of Natural History, Series 11, 13 (102): 361 - 392. http: // dx. doi. org / 10.1080 / 00222934608654562" type="journal article" year="1946">
Barnard, 
<date box="[735,796,336,362]" pageId="2" pageNumber="3" value="1946">1946</date>
</bibRefCitation>
” as well.
</paragraph>
